+  'Analysis summary for ds001_prostate',
+  '',
+  `I analyzed 50,000 prostate-cancer records. The overall objective_response rate was ${pp(outcomeRate)}. Effects below are signed absolute changes in objective_response probability unless otherwise stated. Main-effect models adjusted for age, ECOG performance status, mCRPC, visceral metastases, PSA, Gleason score, albumin, LDH, 6-month weight loss, CRP, NLR, all treatment flags, and key biomarker flags. Interaction models report treatment-subgroup risk-difference interactions.`,
